{"tid":415540,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本東北11日自駕遊行程求意見","createTime":"2017-09-27T05:08:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-29T06:31:42.000Z","uid":26766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5e313a2b3ab7e6acdbf36b727d561c2ec4c45ba8","tid":415540,"uid":26766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T05:08:26.000Z","msg":"今次主要會去買個縣,仙台＞岩手＞青森＞秋田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每個縣會玩兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay1仙台:兩點到東京預四點拎到車即刻揸去仙台,然後仙台酒店附近搵間居酒屋食個晚餐就休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay2仙台：松島町＞大崎市（鳴子峽）＞白石市（藏王狐狸村）<br />\n<br />\nDay3岩手：一關市（嚴美溪同猊鼻溪）＞花卷溫泉<br />\n<br />\nDay4岩手：岩手郡（東北富士山）＞久慈市（夫妻岩）<br />\n<br />\nDay5青森：八戶市＞十和田（奧入瀨溪流）<br />\n<br />\nDay6青森:弘前市＞津輕郡<br />\n<br />\nDay7秋田：男鹿半島＞秋田市<br />\n<br />\nDay8秋田：橫手市＞仙北（混浴溫泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\nDay9群馬：呢個已經有計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay10千葉：呢個想問下咁多位巴打千葉有無咩地方好去,純粹駁腳用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay11:中午機返香港<br />\n<br />\n我想問下咁多位巴打秋田縣好似比較小景點,係咪可以抽一日去山形？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該咁多位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1291fb540fdad65e910cc4dedbffe8d7ef7f4054","tid":415540,"uid":26766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T05:10:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a0965fe04f280b0339a1fa5247da16e5227511","tid":415540,"uid":26766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T05:12:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid